The paper deals with the problem of sampling numbers, which is a fundamental problem in computer science and falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and parallel algorithms (cs.DC). The paper also discusses load balancing and parallelization, which are topics in parallel computing (cs.PF) and distributed computing (cs.Distributed). The use of vectorization on SIMD units or GPUs suggests a focus on numerical analysis (cs.NA).
